----[ Purpose

    Simple Spike Remover for Cacti Graphs
    
----[ Features

    Removes Spikes using Ajax Callbacks.  Two methods are available, they are Standard Deviation and Variance

----[ Installation

    Install just like any other 2.x plugin, just throw it in the plugin directory,
    in the spikekill folder and then 'Install' and 'Enable' it.  Don't remember to give yourself
    permission to use it.
    
----[ Possible Bugs?
   
    If you figure out this problem, let me know!!!

----[ Future Changes
    
    Got any ideas or complaints, please e-mail me!

